      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not really about slowing down or reflecting. its more like... looking at a movie that's already finished. the credits are rolling and the lights are coming up in the theater. you don't stay in your seat once the screen goes dark, right? you just leave. i feel like i'm just waiting for the signal to finally head home.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
